T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"襲擊美國公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b14de2eecafd96d9f7d1d683f45a42c457971dc","tid":1252820,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:28:23.000Z","msg":"香港911<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f478d8580bc8d12833264a8464550c026d1653","tid":1252820,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"外交事件喎<br />\n香港警犬公然襲擊美國公民，險致殘廢<br />\n有冇巴打推件事畀美國政府知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429ae145442efa49b1711e7d22a13557966cb067","tid":1252820,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:37:53.000Z","msg":"追究暴徒法律責任！"}]}